To install, include jQuery & jQuery.nowPlaying.

Add the following to your $(document).ready();

 $('.nowPlaying').nowPlaying({
  number:3, // Number of songs to display.
  username:'kylehotchkiss', // Your username.
  apikey:'please_insert_api', // Your API key.
 });

And this to your document:

 <div class="nowPlaying">
  <div class="lfm_item">
   <div class="lfm_art">
    <a href="#"></a>
    <div class="lfm_playing" title="now playing!"></div>
   </div>
   <div class="lfm_song"></div>
   <div class="lfm_artist"></div>
   <div class="lfm_album"></div>
   <div class="clear"></div>
  </div>
 </div>

Now tada, You got music!
